{"title":"只有枪口对枪口","authors":["梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":11,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有枪口对枪口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国侵略者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸出长长的黑手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手里挥舞着凶器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想逼越南人民低头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知抽刀断水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只能使那水更流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知投弹灭火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只当火上又加油。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒火熊熊燃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒涛声声吼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涛声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传遍了全世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火焰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮我家门口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心也高飞远走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去参加援越抗美的战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对这个共同的死敌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁都有共同的深仇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它制造的锁链，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"套过我们的脚手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它制造的枪弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透过我们的胸口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的军靴曾四处践踏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还梦想独霸全球。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能够呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一万个不能够！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站起来的革命人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从不怕雨暴风骤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中越人民都知道该怎样对付这只野兽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有刀尖对刀尖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪口对枪口！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两国呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山靠山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山高情谊厚；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两国呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水连水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水长同源头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山样的肩并肩；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水样的手拉手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山高耸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水涌流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌寇见了也发抖……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}